{"word":"σπαρτιᾶτις","slug":"σπαρτιᾶτις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σπαρτιᾶτις</b></el> <el>(σπανισᾶτις, ιδος,) </el><p/>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>γυνή</el>) <i>a Spartan woman</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>χώρα</el>) <i>Laconia</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>; also as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <el>Σπ. γυνή, χθών, γῆ</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}